description:
EuroPark mobile app provides fast way to find a parking lot in Riga at a favorable cost and lets you pay for it. Using EuroPark mobile app is simple and convenient. 
EuroPark mobile app gives you option to look at the city map, browse zones and tariffs. It will find your location by using GPS. App allows you to register multiple cars at the same time and lets you pay for them simultaneously.
EuroPark is available for free.

How to use EuroPark app:
    • Download application;
    • Read and accepts Terms & Conditions;
    • Follow the registration steps;
    • Find the parking lot you need;
    • Register your car;
    • Pay for parking;

Download EuroPark app.
